name: tibum residency. first edition
description: The residency is an online program in which the participants will be instigated to take a deep dive in NFTs. We are looking for projects that will bring freshness into the crypto world. All residents will be encouraged to experiment with NFTs, to create art, to develop codes and solutions, to think about ways to educate about NFTs and blockchain, to build international communities and to make connections with one another.
